quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  27,45,"And assuredly We sent unto the Thamud their brother Saleh saying: worship Allah. Then lo! they became two parties contending"
  27,46,"He said: O my people! wherefore seek ye to hasten the evil before the good? Wherefore ask ye not forgiveness of Allah, that haply ye may be shewn mercy"
  27,47,"They said: we augur ill of thee and of those who are with thee. He said: your augury is with Allah. Aye! ye are a people being tested"
  27,48,"And there were nine of a group in the City, who spread corruption in the land and rectified not"
  27,49,"They said: swear one to anot her by God that we shall surely fall upon him and his household by night and thereafter we shall surely say unto his heir; We witnessed not the destruction of his household, and verily we are truthtellers"
  27,50,"And they plotted a plot, and We plotted a plot, while they perceived it not"
  27,51,"So behold thou how was the end of their plotting: verily We annihilated them and their nation all together"
  27,52,"So yonder are their houses overturned, for they did wrong. Verily, herein is a sign unto a people who know"
  27,53,And We delivered those who believed and were wont to fear
  27,54,"And Lut! what time he said unto his people: commit ye indecency while ye see"
  27,55,Would ye go in lustfully unto men instead of women? Aye! ye are a people addicted to ignorant ways